node.text:
🍣Bagging a great meal at home with all our favourite sushi💗 It’s been quite some time since we last had sashimi and sushi so we were thoroughly satisfied🥰⁣
⁣
Enjoy @sushirosingapore delightful platters from only $11.10 with a variety of offerings featuring salmon belly, shrimp, grilled eel and more on @grabfoodsg and @foodpandasg delivered right to your doorsteps. Takeaway menu differs so visit their ig for more details 💗⁣
